snippet.title: Cannibal Cuisine I Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Indulge your insatiable appetite for fresh co-op cooking games with Cannibal Cuisine, releasing on May 20! Wishlist now on Steam for PC, or pre-order for Nintendo Switch and get a 25% discount!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1136020/Cannibal_Cuisine

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/cannibal-cuisine-switch

Fight tourists to collect their meats, use special voodoo powers for healing, cooking or combat, and face end of stage challenge levels that will test more than your culinary capabilities! Play the 24 level story campaign with up to 4 chefs, or engage in competitive versus mode cooking contests. 

#CannibalCuisine #CookingGame #NintendoSwitch

Follow our meaty Social Media channels:
-Twitter: http://twitter.com/rocket_vulture
-Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/
-Reddit: http://www.reddit.com/r/CannibalCuisine
-Discord: https://discord.com/invite/XEagpXt

Want to know more? Take a look at our website:
http://www.rocketvulture.com

About the developers:
Rocket Vulture is an independent game development studio based in Diegem, Belgium and the creators of Cannibal Cuisine for Steam & Nintendo Switch!
